动力学原则不再适用，要改用轨道动力学来分析弹道了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-ca9651fbb61af6440622854ad31c0bad_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "231 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445946498"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgaGt5dvTipsgEAMaCDYxMzc3ODM5IOf20oEGMAI4gwFAGHIJNDQ1OTQ2NDk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1614139311.9697464", "card_id": "Q_446063707", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "员工实名举报中国人寿大量造假，真实情况可能是怎样的？这一现象在保险行业普遍吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "黑龙江女员工 @兔宝宝 1988Z 实名举报公司大量造假。这位工作了十六年的女员工发文举报该公司总经理为了完成公司保费任务，套取公司奖金，绩效以及达成自己的职务晋升等违规行为。兔宝宝 1988Z：实名举报中国人寿保险公司领导造假贪污，黑龙江和黑河银保监局为什么不处理、不作为？员工实名举报中国人寿大量造假，是反腐倡廉的反照"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2d655022c8a877594c8fa98bb77251b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "226 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446063707"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IgaGt5dvTipsgEAMaCDYxNDAzODQ4INnb1oEGMAE4TkAZcgk0NDYwNjM3MDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1614139311.9702713", "card_id": "Q_440621192", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 198}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《斗破苍穹》的药老让人喜欢，而《斗罗大陆》的大师（玉小刚）让人讨厌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc467f685409db9bc6d26aff0f1bf65f_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "210 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/440621192"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgaGt5dvTipsgEAMaCDYwMTkzNzU1IL7jqYAGMA840QNAGnIJNDQwNjIxMTkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1614139311.9706106", "card_id": "